    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><ul><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><strong>C: Copycats</strong>. They follow the pack from behind, and avoid taking too much risks. They have a fast-follower strategy. Their work still contributes to research reproducibility, and demonstrates their ability to keep up with fast-paced research.</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
